{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"载歌行","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":6,"day":26}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"载歌行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载歌行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔并题黄胄同志画的《载歌行》〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人也有花园了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天山好像白玉桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥的那边挂苹果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥的这边挂葡萄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东山上雪燕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西山上云雀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一座桥上聚会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞哟！舞哟！唱哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"维吾尔也有丰年了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山也要大声笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果子叮叮当当响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们裙衫索索飘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卖身契，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奴隶印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴依再也梦不着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血泪树上红灯照。〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁滩上开花了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天山乐得像只鸟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟飞花笑山舞蹈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱哟！舞哟！飞哟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山有千重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路有千条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党指的山最高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席指的路最好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕“巴依”，维吾尔语的意思是地主。过去戈壁滩上的石头、水和野草，巴依也要霸占；买卖奴隶时，在奴隶的脊背上打上火印。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伊犁吐鲁番圩子有一棵“血泪树”，树上吊死过成百的佃户。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天池和长虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔老兵新歌〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶天山雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩挑关外风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扁担和水桶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不减当年勇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水桶像天池，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扁担像长虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕白宫那大“虫”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石海里我们播种。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石河子波飞浪涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山下万马腾空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰峰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"着你来摘雪莲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"着你来作丹枫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新疆石河子农场一位老干部的办公室里，放着扁担和水桶。这个印象我一直不忘，使我写了这首短歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔柯尔克孜族一位山村女教师，她的名字叫“月亮”（阿伊尼莎）〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮呵树是你的门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮呵山是你的家；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柯尔克孜这一个民族，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她是你亲生的妈妈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一群娃娃们像鸽子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扑扑扑飞到山崖下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用智慧的果子饲养他们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使他们长得像彩霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你取下了白头纱——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见祖国这颗新月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在和红领巾把手拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读一页新的历史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲一篇新的童话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开放吧你的花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔答三位青年〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开放吧，你的花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大时代任你来描画；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白杨为你作卫士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红柳为你作篱笆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根子扎在天山下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篝火红、笑声欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试弹一曲冬不拉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹿不攀的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种上包谷和芝麻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅花鹿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野生马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也捉来骑上它。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞白雪、唱红霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞砂走石算个啥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁门关上把门开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放被囚的玛洛莎。〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青纱帐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿锦缎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送她一匹作头纱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花鞍子、枣红马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驮来金钥匙一大把；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问金钥匙是啥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锄头枪杆手上拿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红的云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红的霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织一面红旗满天挂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命人、乐哈哈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自信是无敌于天下；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的本色就是诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的生涯才是画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一座座、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原始森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任战士来作巨厦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开放吧、你的花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春之火燃烧吧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把生命编成弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把戈壁当琵琶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这五个手指，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像五条大河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把整个的旧世界冲垮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初到新疆时，有三位青年同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送来他们自己种的瓜果；临别时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又送来他们三人写的诗歌。我用这"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支歌来回赠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕传说过去新疆有两件珍宝，一件是头上的绿宝珠，阿尔泰戴上了。另一件是金钥匙，要给塔里木，可是被玛洛莎姑娘丢失了，玛洛莎就被囚在塔里木。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}